{"tid":1596930,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"紅軍申請「利物浦」專利商標失敗","createTime":"2019-09-26T17:16:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-27T00:56:41.000Z","uid":16659,"like":7,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"80c515506a81cac9aaa8eeeb52bc303c64102b82","tid":1596930,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T17:16:54.000Z","msg":"【Now Sports-體育】利物浦未能成功申請將「利物浦」作為球會的專利商標，但強調仍會繼續爭取，並會積極打擊侵犯知識產權的人。<br />\n<br />\n英超球隊利物浦早前向英國知識產權局申請將「Liverpool」這位個字作為球會足球產品和服務的註冊商標，然而當局考慮到「利物浦」作為一個城市的地理意義更為重要，再加上比較過英國其他以地方名命球會商標的註冊情況，紅軍的申請最終被拒。<br />\n<br />\n利物浦行政總裁摩亞（Peter Moore）說：「我們強調提出申請是出於真誠，唯一目的是保護和促進球會及其支持者的最大利益。事已至此球會將接受判決，尊重裁決精神，我亦想藉此機會感謝過程中與我們一起努力的所有人，亦想感謝商人們及各個球會的支持。」<br />\n<br />\n利物浦是英超數一數二的老牌大球會，以紅軍名字牟利的商人可謂多不勝數，儘管這次申請私有化「利物浦」不成功，但紅軍強調仍會致力追查那些侵犯知識產權牟利的不法商人，並敦促有關當局採取果斷的執法行動。<br />\n<br />\n圖片來源 : 球會官網圖片"},{"pid":"2cd699e49683e6e47c9710d1d23900ec26853944","tid":1596930,"uid":16659,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T17:17:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://media.giphy.com/media/U8YkkYuoVADVrkVrvA/giphy.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.giphy.com%2Fmedia%2FU8YkkYuoVADVrkVrvA%2Fgiphy.gif&h=1ccc3ed0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://media.giphy.com/media/TfS90uxi84zHpOpfjt/giphy.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.giphy.com%2Fmedia%2FTfS90uxi84zHpOpfjt%2Fgiphy.gif&h=6214c91a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n利記<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27755e155f77b963914d8e61df8c2c2cc5dd9c35","tid":1596930,"uid":145021,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T17:22:15.000Z","msg":"城市名都想專利化 痴撚咗線咩"},{"pid":"287b93629823ed4beb069159bd827543ce5d7dc6","tid":1596930,"uid":8636,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T17:32:47.000Z","msg":"痴撚線<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfd60e28167a1c2edd489950659aae4b875e2991","tid":1596930,"uid":159400,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T18:59:43.000Z","msg":"Liverpool fc啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8def945766047377f45a7a8de838401f8d6adfc","tid":1596930,"uid":67225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T23:25:16.000Z","msg":"球會&gt;城市<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b0ce87313051cf784114adf111d45a0e58165d4","tid":1596930,"uid":206337,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T00:20:04.000Z","msg":"猁狗又然<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0c728e1861bc6f4d36674172bf76a2233887134","tid":1596930,"uid":53062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T00:24:39.000Z","msg":"咁惡，同Amazon搶Amazon森林名有咩分別"},{"pid":"ac0014a1bb5b6b4d54ae3d297a3e3d7912a695a6","tid":1596930,"uid":10757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T00:45:41.000Z","msg":"惡撚到<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/dead.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de58f29a797ce7de7f3442656d2d5aceb55938ea","tid":1596930,"uid":67225,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T00:56:41.000Z","msg":"贏左歐聯真係唔同d<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}